          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced onion</strong> and<strong> chopped tomato </strong>and cook for 3-4 min or until beginning to soften</p><p>Grate the <strong>chestnut mushrooms</strong></p>",
